fields.title: Top Gun: Maverick
fields.review: Awesome thrill ride with an exhilarating aerial combat scenes.

fields.title: Five Feet Apart
fields.review: Interesting. Did a good job, though not 100% accurate, to potray CF in a movie

fields.title: Inside Out
fields.review: As usual, Disney does not disappoint. Quite interesting how they wrapped up human emotions in a cartoon.

fields.title: Spirited Away
fields.review: Interesting story line. The graphics were very beautfiul and mesmerizing for a movie made in 2001.

fields.title: Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows
fields.review: Entertaining sequel from the first film. The sets were spectacular and cinematography was at its finest.

fields.title: Alice in Wonderland
fields.review: Exciting fantasy film with jaw-dropping sets and visuals.

fields.title: Maleficent
fields.review: Another viewpoint from the Sleeping Beauty film. Some scenes may be scary for little kids however the special effects were impressive.

fields.title: The Invisible Man
fields.review: Main character made the film very engaging. The plot was good and the tension was kept throughout the film.
